HEADWORD: Motiveless
<hw>Mo"tive*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Destitute of a motive; not
incited by a motive.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Mo"tive*less*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms> <rj><au>G. Eliot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
